      "writtenOn": "2026-04-21T16:53:17Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This came because I\u0027m personally reviewing a lot of patches with AI hallucinations and it\u0027s taking considerable time.  Having an attribution would allow me to prioritize appropriately, and know when I\u0027m dealing with an LLM versus a human, and review accordingly.",
