      "writtenOn": "2026-04-21T11:58:40Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "In place of \"should\" I\u0027d prefer \"can\". A lot of new tools, like IBM Bob, utilize dynamic models based on the query so it\u0027s not possible to know which model is used for each assist. Also, I just think in general adding this Assited-by should be optional.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 29,
        "startChar": 66,
        "endLine": 29,
        "endChar": 73
      },
      "revId": "96e8aa85d7872b993a2ac5871b7a77f2e4855a08",
